{"type": "article", "id": 27401, "title": "狗窝沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-27T06:54:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 122, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171455KkHUA6qu8C31SfwZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>宠物也是家庭的一员，越来越多的设计师尝试着让家具能同时满足人类和宠物的需求。<a href=\"http://www.munseungji.com/\">Seungji Mun</a> 设计的这张沙发与平时安置在家中其他地方的狗屋结合在了一起，开放的设计让狗狗们可以很方便地攀爬玩耍，同时也拉近了它们和主人间的距离，看上去非常温馨。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171453cNdTKmDwasHZUpS0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171454okhnTGDtiMqzuy1v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171454fEN9J5TIahM0bmgj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171454IVgKaLAZHmkcvFYX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}